flowchart LR
  Search[Public component search] --> Session[JSF session and ViewState]
  Session --> Select[Select semantic result]
  Select --> Detail[Turma detail POST]
  Detail --> Parse[Parse semantic fields]
  Parse --> Store[Cache and catalog upsert]
  Session -. failure .-> Fallback[Manual data preserved]
  Detail -. failure .-> Fallback
  Parse -. missing field .-> Fallback
